sentences: The ASEC analysis team has recently discovered the distribution of Emotet through link files (.lnk). The malware has been steadily distributed in the past, but starting from April, it was found that the Emotet downloader uses Excel files as well as link files (.lnk).
One feature that the secured EML files share is that they all disguise themselves as replies to the users email to distribute the malware strain.
